Sapphire is dried, sieved cannabis also known as 'kief', referring to the granular/powdery accumulation of trichome heads, which are the resin glands where cannabinoids and terpenes live. It's the dry sift process that separates the trichome heads from the plant, minimizing the amount of plant material in the end product. Kief has many different uses -- you can sprinkle it onto your bowl, add it to your roll, cook with it, press it into hash or heat press it into rosin. Sapphire is a powerhouse cannabis product with extremely high THC potency. Recommended for experienced cannabis consumers only.

Bubba presents flavours and aromas reminiscent of spicy earth (caryophyllene) gassy hops (humulene) and creamy coffee (bisabolol).

Pure Sunfarms' cut of Pink Kush from BC's Vancouver Island is a coastal relative of the legendary OG Kush. This special strain is beloved across Canada for its strong aromas, colourful flowers and high THC potential. Beneath a thick coating of trichomes, the dense and round buds feature forest green leaves, often with a purple hue, mixed with dark amber pistils. Grown in a high-tech greenhouse in the Fraser Valley, each bud is carefully trimmed and hand-groomed, dried and cured to precise standards. Pink Kush showcases gassy aromas of white pepper, orange, butterscotch, coffee, earth and grapefruit, the result of a rich combination of terpenes that includes caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, bisabolol, and limonene.

Motor Breath is a combination of two classic cultivars producing a mix of SFV OG Kush with Chemdog gas. The bud structure is tight and medium sized, drenched in trichomes and crystals. With flavours of earthy lemon with notes of citrus and gas, it produces a smooth, heavy-hitting indica smoke, with flavours of citrus and diesel exhales. Expect to have the best of indica and sativa.

Sitka Weed Works Motor Breath is a combination of two classic cultivars producing a mix of SFV OG Kush with Chemdog gas. The bud structure is tight and medium sized, drenched in trichomes and crystals. It has flavours of earthy lemon with notes of citrus and gas. It produces a smooth, heavy-hitting indica smoke, with flavour of citrus and diesel exhales.

Micro producer Quadessence has done it again with this mastery of Black Triangle. The plant care Quadessence exhibits is second to none. Spending up to 20 hours per day in their micro-facility grow rooms, each plant gets the unique care it needs, right down to hand watering each plant every single day. The four-week long hang time and cure is the cherry on the top. The love can truly be felt when trying their Black Triangle. Each pouch is hand packed to ensure the quality of the flower isn't compromised and the trichomes not disturbed. Quadessence wants you to enjoy the flower as close to being on the plant as possible. Crossing Florida's famous Triangle Kush with an '88 G13 Hash Plant, the flower is packed with terpenes and note of citrus, pine, earth and hash spice, making for a refreshing flavour profile that comes in thick.

Brace yourself!! If you think the Titanic took a hard hit from ice, look out! Premium Micro Producer Craft Kings has done it again, knocking it out of the park with Ice Wreck. Craft Kings took this strain to the limit, allowing it to run a full 10-week flower cycle, and it paid off. The nugs stacked early and kept growing to produce huge colourful buds with purple undertones, coated in sugary trichomes. The nose is insane! As per norm, the beautiful flower was hang dried and cured for three weeks until the perfect snap, then hand trimmed by legacy trimmers. This memorable strain is a combination of resinous Ice and Landrace-descended Trainwreck. Ice Wreck offers a rich, earthy aroma. Each pouch is hand packed to ensure the flower is as premium as the day it was taken down, and you get what you deserve......the perfect experience.

Premium Micro Producer Craft Kings has done it again with their Sour OG Cheese. Sour OG Cheese crosses a J's Gold and Citral Skunk strain and Colin OG. Known for its chunky, colourful flowers, this strain produces a noticeable funk of cheese alongside a sour, musky and floral aroma. Craft Kings took their time with the flowering cycle, letting it go a full 10 weeks to get everything out of the plant. Hand harvesting and four-week dry/cure time, followed by one week of burping takes it to the next level. And of course then the trimmers were brought in to hand trim each nug to ensure every trichome is preserved. Craft Kings had a hoot growing the Sour OG Cheese. Each Pouch is carefully packed to ensure you get the experience you deserve. Treat yourself, you will love it.

Micro Producer KnL Cannabis did what they do best......bring out the flavor! And Wow,  did they do an incredible job with their Strawberry Lemonade. This cross between Sour Lemon OG and Strawberry Cough won 2016 Best Sativa at the Hight Times Cannabis Cup. Strawberry Lemonade is perfect for daytime hike or night out with friends. Strawberry Lemonade provides a wonderful scent of strawberries, sour lemon, and other fresh citrus fruits. The flavor of fresh sweet strawberries and zest of lemons really gets you going. KnL's small batch crops allow them to really focus on the terpenes and flavor profiles for which they have become well known for. Each pouch is hand packed by our team to ensure you get the experience you deserve.

Premium Micro Producer Quadessence has nailed another Quad with their Dragon Fruit Mintz. This cross of Snow Lotus x  Silver Haze x Kush Mints is perfect for the afternoon and a great evening with friends! Dragon Fruit Mints has a delightful fragrance. It contains citrusy, tart lemon and lime notes along with a touch of sweetness. Delectable hints of ripe, summer fruit run throughout the full-bodied smoke. Other smells also appear, including earth, herb, pine, and a slight edge of diesel. The flavour has a massive hit of sweet, burst of intense fruit with citrus notes and warm earth, with a hint of herb and light spice. The flowers themselves are lush and colourful, with huge stacked nugs, and thick layer of sticky crystalline trichomes. Quadessence did what they do best, which is love this plant. This strain was allowed to run its full course with daily hand watering. Once ready, the flower was hand harvested to ensure none of the pistols or trichomes were touched. The flower was hang dried for 3 weeks, followed by a 2 week burp and cure. Once at the perfect moisture level, the hand trimming team come in for the final stages. Each pouch is hand filled to ensure the highest quality and guarantee the experience you deserve.

Grab one and go... where no one has gone before? We'll leave that up to you. Wham. Zing. Whoosh. Everything just got better.

LA Confidential and Black Cherry Soda meld together in the LA Soda Jet Pack from BZAM, featuring four high-THC 0.5g pre-rolls of LA Soda infused with 99 per cent THCA. Indica-dominant with berry, sweet, cherry and pine flavours from limonene, linalool and caryophyllene, these pre-rolls contain whole milled flower only, so hold the shake and get ready to pop off with the LA Soda Jet Pack. Wham. Zing. Whoosh. Everything just got better.

With lineage featuring legendary Sour Diesel and Do-Si-Dos (Leafly's 2021 Strain of the Year), Diesel Dough is off to a great start as TABLE TOP's first pitch in the pre-roll game. Throw in high THC and some nutty, diesel, sugary and flowery notes from caryophyllene, myrcene and limonene and these whole-flower, sativa-dominant pre-rolls are ready for your regular lineup. You gonna hit it out of the park or what? It's Got Legs.

BZAM and Dunn Cannabis present a multi-pack of 12 pre-rolls with high THC and two experiences to choose from. Go for Fresh Squeezed OG from BZAM if you're into a hybrid strain with citrus, herbal, spicy, sour and fruity vibes from caryophyllene, limonene and farnesene. Or, try Vanilla Berry Pie from Dunn Cannabis - an indica-dominant hybrid with a sweeter profile featuring vanilla and cookie flavours with hints of mint and spice courtesy of caryophyllene, limonene and myrcene. The pack includes six x 0.5g pre-rolls of each, so there's plenty of opportunity to compare notes.
Strain_(Sub 3 Category): Fresh Squeezed OG x Vanilla Berry Pie

Long Product Description: K-Smorz and Citrus Rush are together at last in this multi-pack of 12 pre-rolls from -ness, including six 0.5g pre-rolls of each strain, both with high THC. K-Smorz is a sweet and nutty hybrid with limonene, myrcene and caryophyllene imparting cookie dough and graham cracker notes. Indica-dominant Citrus Rush brings the zing with sugary citrus flavour and a dash of earthy skunk from terpinolene, caryophyllene and limonene. Whether you like it sweet, sour, or both, this multi-pack brings the flavour. Explore Your -ness.

BZAM's Member That OG is a balanced hybrid cross between Member Berry 21 and Temple Kush that was discovered during BZAM's internal pheno-hunt. It's got high THC and sweet, tart, berry and floral flavours from a terpene profile starring myrcene, caryophyllene and limonene. Grown in Alberta and known for its deep purple buds threaded with subtle orange pistils, this strain offers much more than just a memberable name. Wham. Zing. Whoosh. Everything just got better.

What do you get when Peanut Butter Breath and Miracle Alien Cookies meet each other on the pheno-hunting ground? BZAM's newest creation: Peanut Butter MAC! Grown in Alberta, hang dried and hand trimmed, this high-THC, indica-dominant flower delivers nutty, earthy and herbal flavours courtesy of terpinolene, caryophyllene and limonene. A successful hunt indeed. Wham. Zing. Whoosh. Everything just got better.

One of the first releases from the BZAM and Dunn Craft Series, Cake Crasher has a lot to brag about. High THC in a tight range, hang dried and hand trimmed, this small-batch, BC-grown indica-dominant beauty is more than just a multi-hyphenate. A cutting from Seed Junky's JBeezy, it's a hybrid of Wedding Cake and Wedding Crasher that delivers sweet, gassy and grape flavours from caryophyllene, myrcene and limonene. Look for the grower, drying, curing and trimming details printed right on the pouch before you give it a spin.

Part of our ongoing pheno-hunt, Rainmaker from -ness is a hybrid strain with high THC and flavours of citrus, skunk, lime, cheese and a touch of sourness from caryophyllene, myrcene and limonene. Grown indoors in Alberta, this strain has Citral Skunk and Mandarin Sunset lineage and features sticky, forest green buds coated in crystal trichomes and delicate orange hairs. Get your gumboots ready, Rainmaker is about to drop! Explore Your -ness.

The highest THC flower from -ness to date, Red Eye OG is sure to steal the show with her equally powerful earthy, citrus and sour flavours from caryophyllene, farnesene and myrcene. She's got Bubba and King Kush in her genes, she's grown indoors and she's about to make a strong debut in Alberta. Explore Your -ness.

Bringing plenty of sour power from its East Coast Sour Diesel and Double Sour OG lineage, BC-grown Secret Garden (Rebel Sour) from -ness is a high-THC hybrid ready to get 'em salivating! Caryophyllene, limonene and farnesene add earthy, diesel and herbal notes to its sour flavour profile. The buds offer amazing trichome density and structure and they're hang dried and hand trimmed with care. Don't miss out on this small batch for sour lovers. Explore Your -ness.

Bringing strong citrus aromas rounded out with earthy, musky and sweet notes from caryophyllene, terpinolene and limonene, Lemon Cheesecake from TABLE TOP is a zesty one. This sativa-dominant strain is hybrid, greenhouse grown, offering high THC and medium-to-large sized buds packed into a convenient 28g package. If you've ever wanted to try a cross between Lemon Skunk and Cheese and prefer to buy your weed by the ounce, this one's for you! It's Got Legs.

Looking for an ounce of something pungent with high THC? Does TABLE TOP have a strain for you! It's called Lemon Diesel and it's packed with lemony, peppery and diesel-y flavours from caryophyllene, myrcene and limonene. From the geniuses at Green Lantern Seeds, Lemon Diesel is a cross between California Sour and Lost Coast OG and it's grown in a hybrid greenhouse. We're just stoked we got to say pungent and diesel-y in the same breath. Let us have this moment. And try the Lemon Diesel. Thank you. It's Got Legs.

Zombie Kush? A cool name for sure but there's a lot more to like about this strain from TABLE TOP. A cross between Amnesia, Lavender Kush and Bubba Kush created by Ripper Seeds, Zombie Kush is a high-THC, indica-dominant hybrid that also brings high terpene content. Terpinolene, myrcene and ocimene round out its top terpenes, bringing bold earthy, berry and flowery flavours. Best of all, it won't eat your brains! It's Got Legs.

WAGNERS Soap Bar Hash is a traditional UK style of hash popularized in the late 1980s and early 1990s. Synonymous with the rise of Brit Pop, Soap Bar was the go-to product for a generation of consumers. It's created using an old school, solventless hash production method where trichomes are sifted and then pressed together using heat until we're left with a light brown bar of hash. Upon heating, the product will 'fluff up' and can be easily crumbled into a joint or bowl. The name is derived from old-school production methodologies, when hash was pressed in 250g bars, the same weight as a bar of soap.

Our Old School Pressed Hash is created as the name suggests, using an old school solventless method. We start by sifting our fresh, indoor grown flower to collect the trichomes. Then with gentle heat we press them together to create a consistent, slightly sticky hash with the colour of cacao-forward chocolate. The way the product was always intended to look, feel and smell, our Old School Pressed Hashish packs a flavourful punch that will take you back to simpler times.

Blazing Saddles is a connoisseur-grade pre-roll that delivers quality without burning a hole through your pocket. Blueberry Fuego is a very rare and unique cultivar. This particular pheno was selected by Noble Growth and boasts heavy blueberry dessert terps. Although what type of berry this strain actually smells like is widely debated, blueberry and blackberries come to mind first. Every waft of Blueberry Fuego feels like you're getting slapped in the face with a blueberry muffin. Consumers can expect smooth and creamy muffin terps at first with a strong blueberry aftertaste. This strain was bred by Seed Junky Genetics, crossing the infamous Slurricane with Symbiotic Genetic's Wedding Crasher. After receiving a small five-pack of seeds as a gift at the 2018 Emerald Cup, Noble Growth selected this particular pheno and coined it 'Blueberry Fuego' (Slurricane and Wedding Crasher).

Long Product Description: Ladies look out, here comes Poolboy Bruce. This powerful strain is made from dense buds resulting in a THC content that reaches nearly 25%. Bruce believes life is all about balance and that's why he's here to bring you the perfect combination of Sativa and Indica effects. Fun facts about Bruce he tastes of a pungent citrus but compared to his smell, tastes a little earthier (loves gardening) and less sweet (not too big of a sweet tooth on this guy). Now I know you're all thinking Wow Bruce sounds amazing. Where in the world did he come from? Well, bred by Jason Holck of Dark Horse Genetics, he was cross bred with Strawberry Diesel and OG Kush. Similar to other plants of this strain, it took Bruce 8 to 10 weeks to reach his full potential and let me tell you, he was a sight to behold. Rich magenta hued leaves, bright green buds frosted with large headed trichomes and red hairs. One look and you're thinking Damn, that dude is rad.

Poolboy No, he's PoolKING and he's here to rule your world, baby.
King T is all kinds of suave and cool. This sativa dominant strain, also known as Tutankhamon, has powers only a true ruler could possess and knows exactly how he wants his kingdom to react to him. Of course, his name pays homage to one of Egypt's most mighty Pharaoh's and his strain is just as mighty as the name. As a descendent of AK-47, he is extremely rare and works to create a cerebral effect in all those who come across his power of a near 20% THC level. 
King T has the abilities to make you feel very social, energized and creative. He wants a world where everyone feels good and gets along and because of this, he's ideal to bring out for your daytime activities, exercise, or social events. He can cause red eyes and dry mouth but nothing some modern day eye drops and a sweet cocktail can't fix. All hail the King.
What might a King smell like? Why only the finest citrus and earthy aroma and flavour profile with a sour, skunky touch. Tutankhamun gains this aroma through his 60 day flowering cycle where he produces an abundant amount of cottony, crystal coated buds with lots of trichomes.

Faster than a speeding pre-roll. More powerful than a dab machine. Able to leap tall buildings in a single puff. Look Up high, in the sky, it's a bird, it's a plane, no it's Super Lemon Haze. Bred from Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze, Super Lemon Haze is the undisputed world champion. As a two time Cannabis Cup winner, Super Lemon Haze is a kief caked multi coloured wonder and is always keeping it fresh. Fresher than the pucker of a hundred lemons. This sativa packs an energizing and lively punch and will not disappoint even the most discerning cannabis connoisseurs.  As you'd expect, Super Lemon Haze is a tasty little combo of sweet and lemon tart flavours and aromas. THC can reach as high as that super bird in the sky, and is a high yielding, overachieving bad ass.

This Poolboy is here to bring you the happiest day of your life! Get ready to get stuff done with this Raspberry Cough. When ICE and Cambodian Landrace were cross-bred by growers at Nirvana Seeds, they created a sativa-dominant hybrid that was ready to take on the job. Poolboy Raspberry Cough is a tasty little dude, with a touch of spice to his flavour profile and leaving a nice raspberry aftertaste. The sweet berry also comes out with his scent accompanied by an earthy nuttiness. He can be known to make you cough (hence the last name) but that's hardly a downfall. Easy to grow, flourishing both inside and out, with a pungent odour and a favourable yield, Raspberry Cough can get up to 10 feet tall during its flowering cycle of 9 to 11 weeks. A sweet, complex bud everyone wants to be friends with, you're gonna want this little pre-roll ready for anything life may throw your way!

Poolboy Strawberry Banana definitely isn't employee of the month based on his work ethic and motivation but is he ever sick to chill out with! The indica-dominant hybrid, created by breeders at DNA Genetics in collaboration with Serious Seeds, is a cross between Bubble Gum and Banana Kush. You know strains with names like that are bound to create something delicious and Strawberry Banana definitely lives up to the name. With an appealing sweet and fruity flavour, tasting like berries on the exhale, and unique, strong aroma -- good luck being discreet -- you'll enjoy this easygoing, mellow high right from the first toke. Strawberry Banana is all about taking it slow. Overall, just get ready to wind down with this guy. Strawberry Banana produces small to medium sized flowers with dense buds and a furry coating of white trichomes.
